     <section aria-labelledby="intro-header" class="col-xs-12 main-section" role="region">
      <header class="main-section-header" id="intro-header">
       <h2 class="top">
        Connecting students with opportunities to explore careers, engage in the community, and enrich their education through experiential learning.
       </h2>
      </header>
     </section>
     <section aria-labelledby="main-region" class="col-xs-12 col-sm-7 main-section pull-left" role="region">
      <article class="main-section-content" id="main-region">
       <p>
        The Academic Internship Program allows students to integrate academic theory and ‘real world' practice, engage in research that explores the relationship between the two, and gain hands-on experience in professional settings.
       </p>
       <h2>
        AIP offers:
       </h2>
       <ul>
        <li>
         Academic internships that foster career, personal and academic development
        </li>
        <li>
         Service learning initiatives for faculty interested in integrating a service-related fieldwork component into the curriculum
        </li>
        <li>
         Customized partnerships with campus departments and programs interested in integrating internships with departmental objectives
        </li>
        <li>
         Top notch talent for corporate and community organizations committed to fostering a culture of learning
        </li>
       </ul>
       <h2>
        Get started
       </h2>
       <ul>
        <li>
         <a href="students/apply-aip.html">
          Apply for AIP
         </a>
        </li>
        <li>
         <a href="http://aipinternlink.ucsd.edu" title="InternLink for students">
          Search for an Internship
         </a>
        </li>
        <li>
         <a href="employers/post-an-internship.html">
          Post an Internship Opportunity
         </a>
        </li>
        <li>
         <a href="faculty/faculty-advisor-role.html">
          Serve as a Faculty Advisor
         </a>
        </li>
        <li>
         <a href="faculty/academic-partnerships.html">
          Partner with AIP
         </a>
        </li>
       </ul>
       <h2>
        Programs
       </h2>
       <ul>
        <li>
         <a href="programs/ucdc/index.html">
          UCDC
         </a>
        </li>
        <li>
         <a href="programs/uccs.html">
          UC Center Sacramento
         </a>
        </li>
        <li>
         <a href="students/earn-credit.html">
          Major- and Minor-specific programs
         </a>
        </li>
       </ul>
       <div class="WordSection1">
        <h2>
         Teaching + Learning Commons
        </h2>
        <p>
         <img alt="Decorative" height="109" src="_images/logos/commons logo small.jpg" width="120"/>
        </p>
       </div>
       <p>
        AIP is a unit within the Experiential Learning Hub of the
        <a href="http://commons.ucsd.edu/">
         Teaching + Learning Commons
        </a>
        , which expands our reach across campus and offers new partnership opportunities.
       </p>
       <content-block>
       </content-block>
      </article>
     </section>
     <section aria-labelledby="sidebar-comp" class="col-xs-12 col-sm-5 main-section sidebar pull-right" role="complementary">
      <div id="sidebar-comp">
       <a href="http://aip.ucsd.edu/_files/5%20Things%20for%20Summer%20WI%20update.pdf">
       </a>
       <h2 class="side">
        <a alt="Link to full article" href="http://aip.ucsd.edu/_files/5%20Things%20for%20Summer%20WI%20update.pdf">
         5 Things to do now to Prepare for Summer Research &amp; Internships
        </a>
       </h2>
       <article>
        <img alt="5 Things to do now to Prepare for Summer Research &amp; Internships" class="right" src="_images/5thingsforsummercrop.png"/>
        <p class="p1">
         Many competitive summer opportunities recruit in fall and early winter. Here are 5 things you can do to plan ahead and get ahead!
        </p>
       </article>
       <a href="https://iah.ucsd.edu/academics/undergrad-opportunities/internships.html">
       </a>
       <h2 class="side">
        <a alt="Link to full article" href="https://iah.ucsd.edu/academics/undergrad-opportunities/internships.html">
         Scholarship for Arts &amp; Humanities Interns
        </a>
       </h2>
       <article>
        <img alt="Scholarship for Arts &amp; Humanities Interns" class="right" src="_images/logos/iahlogo.png"/>
        <p class="p1">
         The UC San Diego Institute of Arts &amp; Humanities offers a scholarship to support Arts &amp; Humanities majors in academic internships, or participating in the UCDC or UC Center Sacramento programs. Visit AIP to learn more about these opportunities!
        </p>
       </article>
       <a href="http://aip.ucsd.edu/programs/ucdc/index.html">
       </a>
       <h2 class="side">
        <a alt="Link to full article" href="http://aip.ucsd.edu/programs/ucdc/index.html">
         UCDC Drop-in Hours
        </a>
       </h2>
       <article>
        <img alt="UCDC Drop-in Hours" class="right" src="_images/logos/ucdc logo.jpg"/>
        <p class="p1">
         Drop by AIP to discuss the UCDC program with a Peer Mentor who has participated in the UCDC program! Drop-in Hours are Mondays from 2:00-4:00pm and Thursdays from 1:30-4:00pm.
        </p>
       </article>
       <a href="contact/index.html">
       </a>
       <h2 class="side">
        <a alt="Link to full article" href="contact/index.html">
         Find us in Geisel!
        </a>
       </h2>
       <article>
        <img alt="Find us in Geisel!" class="right" src="_images/geisel.jpg"/>
        <p class="p1">
         AIP is located in the Teaching + Learning Commons @ Geisel Library (lower level).  AIP counselors and Peer Advisers are meet with students to discuss internship goals and options, or help with the application process.  Come to Drop-in Hours, or schedule an appointment.
        </p>
       </article>
       <a href="http://vac.ucsd.edu">
       </a>
       <h2 class="side">
        <a alt="Link to full article" href="http://vac.ucsd.edu">
         AIP on the VAC
        </a>
       </h2>
       <article>
        <img alt="AIP on the VAC" class="right" src="_images/vac.jpg"/>
        <p class="p1">
         Current students: Do you have a question for AIP? Send us a message in the Virtual Advising Center.
        </p>
       </article>
       <a href="http://elt.ucsd.edu/">
       </a>
       <h2 class="side">
        <a alt="Link to full article" href="http://elt.ucsd.edu/">
         Engaged Learning Tools
        </a>
       </h2>
       <article>
        <img alt="Engaged Learning Tools" class="right" src="_images/elt-logo.jpg"/>
        <p class="p1">
         Find opportunities and showcase your internship experience using UCSD's Engaged Learning Tools: the REAL Portal, Enhanced Electronic Transcript, and Co-Curricular Record.
        </p>
       </article>
